Package: vstaskviewer
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Task execution viewer with WebSocket support
 vsTaskViewer is a Go application that starts predefined commands as background tasks and displays their output (stdout/stderr)
 live through a web interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Parameterized tasks with typed parameters
  - Web interface for live task output viewing
  - WebSocket support for real-time streaming
  - JWT authentication
  - Rate limiting and security features
  - Optional TLS/HTTPS support

